Dear The A 1 OrgAdmin,
Org B has approved your invitation for addition to Test Network. Please login to activate their participation in the network.

http://pkb-frontend-8/orgCoord/viewEditOrgNetwork.action

If you have any questions, please call us on 1223 790708 ext: 2 or e-mail help@pkbtest.com.

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
